::KitKat::

She turned to Drillbit on her way inside the base. "Drillbit, would 
you go and escort our fox to the brig below, then take over scanning 
the area on the bridge.  Keep an eye on the Allience base. I don't 
want any suprizes." She smiled at Drillbit and winked. She had that, 
wait till I get you alone, look in her eyes. 

She then went into the base and headed for the conference room. She 
waited for Megatron and Aracnia to join her.  She activated her clone 
and ordered it to stay where it was, in her quarters, until ordered 
otherwise.
